{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/MermaidDiagrams"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiftMarkdownView"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Mermaidダイアグラム"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/MermaidScriptProvider","doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/MermaidScriptSource","doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/CDNMermaidScriptProvider","doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/BundledMermaidScriptProvider","doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/AdaptiveMermaidView","doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/MermaidFallbackView"],"title":"Mermaid ダイアグラム","generated":true,"anchor":"Mermaid-ダイアグラム"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"SwiftMarkdownViewはMermaidダイアグラムをサポートしている。","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"コードブロックの言語に","type":"text"},{"code":"mermaid","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"を指定すると、コードがダイアグラムとしてレンダリングされる。","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AA%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%84%E6%96%B9","text":"基本的な使い方"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["MarkdownView(\"\"\"","```mermaid","graph TD","    A[開始] --> B{判断}","    B -->|はい| C[OK]","    B -->|いいえ| D[キャンセル]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"“””)","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["","## 対応ダイアグラム","","以下のMermaidダイアグラムタイプがサポートされている：","","| タイプ | 説明 | 例 |","|--------|------|-----|","| flowchart | フローチャート | `graph TD` |","| sequence | シーケンス図 | `sequenceDiagram` |","| class | クラス図 | `classDiagram` |","| state | 状態遷移図 | `stateDiagram-v2` |","| gantt | ガントチャート | `gantt` |","| journey | ユーザージャーニー | `journey` |","| timeline | タイムライン | `timeline` |","| mindmap | マインドマップ | `mindmap` |","","## 動作環境","","Mermaidダイアグラムのレンダリングはプラットフォームのバージョンによって異なる：","","### iOS 26+、macOS 26+、tvOS 26+、watchOS 26+","","WebKitを使用したネイティブレンダリングが行われる。","ダイアグラムは完全にインタラクティブに表示され、ライト\/ダークモードに自動対応する。","","### それ以前のバージョン","","フォールバック表示が使用される。","ダイアグラムはコードブロックとして表示され、Mermaidコードがそのまま見える状態になる。","","## ダイアグラムの例","","### フローチャート","","```swift","MarkdownView(\"\"\"","```mermaid","graph LR","    A[入力] --> B[処理]","    B --> C[出力]","    B --> D[ログ]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“””)"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["","### シーケンス図","","```swift","MarkdownView(\"\"\"","```mermaid","sequenceDiagram","    participant User","    participant App","    participant Server","    User->>App: タップ","    App->>Server: リクエスト","    Server-->>App: レスポンス","    App-->>User: 表示"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“””)"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["","### クラス図","","```swift","MarkdownView(\"\"\"","```mermaid","classDiagram","    class Animal {","        +String name","        +makeSound()","    }","    class Dog {","        +bark()","    }","    Animal <|-- Dog"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“””)"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["","### 状態遷移図","","```swift","MarkdownView(\"\"\"","```mermaid","stateDiagram-v2","    [*] --> Idle","    Idle --> Loading: fetch","    Loading --> Success: done","    Loading --> Error: fail","    Success --> [*]","    Error --> Idle: retry"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“””)"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["","## テーマ","","Mermaidダイアグラムはシステムのカラースキームに自動対応する：","","- **ライトモード**: デフォルトのMermaidテーマ","- **ダークモード**: ダークテーマが自動適用","","## パフォーマンス","","Mermaidダイアグラムは内部でWebKitのWebViewを使用してレンダリングされる。","複雑なダイアグラムや多数のダイアグラムを含むドキュメントでは、","パフォーマンスに影響が出る場合がある。","","## 制限事項","","- iOS 26未満ではダイアグラムとしてレンダリングされない","- 非常に大きなダイアグラムはスクロールが必要になる場合がある","- インタラクティブな機能（クリックイベントなど）はサポートされていない"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftmarkdownview\/mermaiddiagrams"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Markdownコードブロック内でMermaidダイアグラムを表示する方法を学ぶ。"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView"]]},"references":{"doc://SwiftMarkdownView/documentation/SwiftMarkdownView/BundledMermaidScriptProvider":{"title":"BundledMermaidScriptProvider","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BundledMermaidScriptProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/BundledMermaidScriptProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"アプリバンドルから読み込む Mermaid スクリプトプロバイダー。"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftmarkdownview\/bundledmermaidscriptprovider","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"BundledMermaidScriptProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://SwiftMarkdownView/documentation/SwiftMarkdownView/AdaptiveMermaidView":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AdaptiveMermaidView","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/AdaptiveMermaidView","type":"topic","title":"AdaptiveMermaidView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS 26 以降でネイティブ WebView を使用し、それ以前はコード表示にフォールバックするアダプティブビュー。"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"AdaptiveMermaidView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftmarkdownview\/adaptivemermaidview"},"doc://SwiftMarkdownView/documentation/SwiftMarkdownView/MermaidScriptProvider":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MermaidScriptProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftMarkdownView\/documentation\/SwiftMarkdownView\/MermaidScriptProvid